{"title":"寿星自叹——观补药广告有感","authors":["杨翰端"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":10,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"寿星自叹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——观补药广告有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨翰端诗  王复羊画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这补药，那补品，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷出面将我请，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电视广告作宣传："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“服用此药保康宁……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东边跑，西边奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得老夫头发昏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕补药没吹完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疲劳过度要丢命……（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}